      "content": "but it's not hope. everything i do just makes it harder. i looked at the bank statement today and then i looked at my kids and i just thought... if i wasn't here, the expenses would be lower, she wouldn't have to work so much, and we wouldnt have to worry about my mistakes anymore. it's just math. it feels like the only logical way to actually help them is to just... stop being part of the problem.",
